snippet.title: Distance - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Debut trailer of my game, Distance! 
Distance is an adventure platforming video game, focused on a young man searching for his brother.
For more information, visit the games GameJolt page here: 
http://gamejolt.com/games/platformer/distance/17089/
